title: Residents: 'Nobody in Wuhan Believes the Official Numbers' of Coronavirus Deaths
description: Multiple reports published on Wednesday quoting residents of Wuhan, China, the city where the coronavirus pandemic originated, found extreme skepticism among locals that the Communist Party's official coronavirus death toll truly reflects the disease's impact…
